name: COVID19SNOMEDValueSetForDiabetesMellitus
title: COVID19 SNOMED Value Set for Diabetes Mellitus
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to type 1, type 2 and unspecified diabetes mellitus and is listed as a chronic metabolic disease on the CDC SARS-CoV-2 hospitalization surveillance case report form.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes type 1, type 2 and unspecified diabetes meliitus, diabetes secondary to another condition (e.g., Diabetes mellitus due to cystic fibrosis) and diabetes terms that secondarily include complications (e.g., Diabetes mellitus type 2 with periodontal disease).),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes terms that solely address diabetic complications (e.g., diabetic nephropathy). It also excludes transient neonatal diabetes, gestational diabetes, type 1 or type 2 diabetes complicating pregnancy, diabetes insipidus, and terms that solely address diabetic complications (e.g., diabetic nephropathy).)
